29
00:02:04,199 --> 00:02:05,919
Tidak mungkin benar-benar
Qiu Yan, 'kan?

30
00:02:07,519 --> 00:02:09,720
Kau bilang kau kenal Qiu Yan.

31
00:02:10,320 --> 00:02:13,160
